{"type": "article", "id": 22189, "title": "3D巧克力人头", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-14T08:23:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606134133f9AkhGQgcRz80nOx.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">巧克力是情人节的必备礼物，也是超市、餐厅不会放过的营销。日本的咖啡馆FabCafe 平时也会提供 3D 打印与激光切割服务，在情人节，他们就设计了与此相关的活动，为女性扫描面部并制作 3D 人脸模型的巧克力。人物的各种表情都被记录下来，让这款巧克力非常独特。这个活动也被延续下来，还可以制作各种糖果，全身扫描，让男女双方互赠礼物。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134132Cov2LXdgKplk0DVu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66530612\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134132rV28jyzuwqDJYSNM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66530612\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134132YKa2EQP0g8LslpO9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63304721\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134133zSMNImyl2RioT6Cv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61770624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}